庭拆細, 結(初婚)/離婚數字係重要指標。<br />\n07～16 結婚(初婚)宗數 ：35,667<br />\n07～16 離婚宗數 ：19,162<br />\n07～16 雙方再婚宗數：7,049<br />\n淨需求47,780, (未計移民增長, 例如專才計劃, 雙非, 來港進修等)<br />\n<br />\n上面講只係減左雙方再婚宗數，一對人結婚(1間)-&gt;離婚(2間)-&gt;再結(4間)-&gt;再離(8間)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0f603d11b7b7fff7f86d08b136ae8e28b5538b","tid":650242,"uid":173015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0624d6d3bf476e35921e76a039fb1f187a60229","tid":650242,"uid":42921,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f6fe9f231eebc969491e6f3ec4859d2ba12f475","tid":650242,"uid":173015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"461cf4950ceec016fd32a0d5ac5d72597e8a6ff5","tid":650242,"uid":42921,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:47:34.000Z","msg":"離婚再結再離就一開八，剛需剛需<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:49:37.000Z","msg":"再結再離都係住番嗰間屋,點開8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T08:05:49.000Z","msg":"但除左人口增長外, 香港既住屋需求仲有家庭拆細, 而時社會普遍共識係&rdquo;結左婚會搬出去住&rdquo;, 而離婚又要分開住, 所以家庭拆細, 結(初婚)/離婚數字係重要指標。<br />\n07～16 結婚(初婚)宗數 ：35,667<br />\n07～16 離婚宗數 ：19,162<br />\n07～16 雙方再婚宗數：7,049<br />\n淨需求47,780, (未計移民增長, 例如專才計劃, 雙非, 來港進修等)<br />\n<br />\n上面講只係減左雙方再婚宗數，一對人結婚(1間)-&gt;離婚(2間)-&gt;再結(4間)-&gt;再離(8間)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T08:56:35.